<br>
More armor/physical weapons.   I'll probably get flamed for this, but I -LIKE- tanking and getting dirty.  If all classes get armor/weapon procs, basically intruding on the casting class-realms, why can't wizards get some sweet armor?  Surely, as the masters of damage, we could come up with SOMETHING to help AVOID damage...after all, we're supposed to know damage and it's many forms the best, right?  <br>
<br>
Tanks get haste gear.  What about gear that drops spell-casting times by .xx seconds?<br>
<br>
Spell-deflection gear?<br>
<br>
Spell-absorbtion gear?  Absorbs offensive spells cast at the wizard into his/her mana pool.<br>
<br>
We're pure damage, effectively...aside from transport.<br>
No pets, no real self-buffs, no real group buffs, no real, well, much of anything besides damage and transport.<br>
<br>
Okay, I knew that when I signed up for this gig.<br>
What I didn't know was the huge amount of down-time<br>
and, for lack of a better word, non-groupability. <br>
<br>
I know that things are in the works, and I'm looking<br>
forward to it - perhaps instead of more &quot;burn burn burn&quot; gear/items/spells/etc, we need some more &quot;fun&quot;<br>
or &quot;crazy&quot; stuff.<br>
<br>
I was terribly bummed when I found out that &quot;Lightning Bolt&quot; looks likes a stupid Fire Bolt.   Or that shock of lightning looks like some Enchanter spell.<br>
<br>
Maybe what we need are some &quot;impressive&quot; spell effects.  Avg power, but just LOOK cool.  It's one <br>
thing to see something burst into flame (from a lightning bolt???) and an entirely other effect to see something's head pop and have it crumple to the ground.<br>
New dead-animations probably aren't possible, but I'm sure you understand the gist of the idea.<br>
<br>
Thanks...<br>
<br>
Peace, love, explosions...<br>
<br>
-Szii/Chifiir <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=396.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=396.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.emailToFriend?topicID=396.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.threadControl?topicID=396.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=396.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=396.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub140.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm60">Graffe Forum News<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General EQ Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcomp